  "captions": {
    "s1": [
      {
        "t0": 0.15,
        "t1": 2.75,
        "text": "Most financial education fails for a simple reason:"
      },
      {
        "t0": 2.75,
        "t1": 5.99,
        "text": "it assumes people are struggling because they don't know enough."
      },
      {
        "t0": 5.99,
        "t1": 6.64,
        "text": "They're not."
      },
      {
        "t0": 6.64,
        "t1": 9.88,
        "text": "They're struggling because the math of their lives doesn't work,"
      },
      {
        "t0": 9.88,
        "t1": 11.83,
        "text": "and nobody built tools for that."
      },
      {
        "t0": 11.83,
        "t1": 13.78,
        "text": "I'm Scott Glasgow, founder of FinMango,"
      },
      {
        "t0": 13.78,
        "t1": 14.75,
        "text": "and we did."
      }
    ],
    "s2": [
      {
        "t0": 0.15,
        "t1": 3.31,
        "text": "We build free, open financial decision tools."
      },
      {
        "t0": 3.31,
        "t1": 6.93,
        "text": "Calculators, simulations, and curriculum designed around real constraints,"
      },
      {
        "t0": 6.93,
        "t1": 8.29,
        "text": "not textbook budgets."
      },
      {
        "t0": 8.29,
        "t1": 14.16,
        "text": "A renter can find out in sixty seconds whether a lease is sustainable."
      },
      {
        "t0": 14.16,
        "t1": 19.13,
        "text": "A first-gen student can compare retirement accounts without a finance degree."
      },
      {
        "t0": 19.13,
        "t1": 22.75,
        "text": "No logins, no paywalls, works on any phone."
      }
    ],
    "s3": [
      {
        "t0": 0.15,
        "t1": 1.81,
        "text": "And this isn't a concept."
      },
      {
        "t0": 1.81,
        "t1": 3.47,
        "text": "We've reached over 100,000 students."
      },
      {
        "t0": 3.47,
        "t1": 5.47,
        "text": "We've run programs in 13 countries."
      },
      {
        "t0": 5.47,
        "t1": 11.11,
        "text": "Our research with Google Health has been used by the WHO, the World Bank, and the IMF."
      },
      {
        "t0": 11.11,
        "t1": 15.43,
        "text": "And our Financial Health Barometer tracks household financial stress in near real time,"
      },
      {
        "t0": 15.43,
        "t1": 19.75,
        "text": "so we know where help is needed before the eviction filings show up."
      }
    ],
    "s4": [
      {
        "t0": 0.15,
        "t1": 4.1,
        "text": "Here's why we scale: our tools are modular and open."
      },
      {
        "t0": 4.1,
        "t1": 8.04,
        "text": "Reaching a new country means translating content, not rebuilding technology,"
      },
      {
        "t0": 8.04,
        "t1": 12.78,
        "text": "and we already have trained ambassadors in 12 countries ready to localize."
      },
      {
        "t0": 12.78,
        "t1": 16.33,
        "text": "This year, 419 people applied for 11 ambassador spots."
      },
      {
        "t0": 16.33,
        "t1": 18.7,
        "text": "The demand exists. The tools exist."
      },
      {
        "t0": 18.7,
        "t1": 23.83,
        "text": "What we need is CGAP's distribution muscle and measurement expertise to connect them."
      },
      {
        "t0": 23.83,
        "t1": 27.38,
        "text": "Pick FinMango, and you're not funding another literacy program."
      },
      {
        "t0": 27.38,
        "t1": 29.75,
        "text": "You're funding infrastructure for financial health."
      }
    ]
  }
